<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(300deg, #c3bcc6, #b9e6e3, rgb(255, 255, 255));
            background-size: 180% 180%;
            animation: gradient-animation 6s ease infinite;
            /* This will hide horizontal scrollbar */
        }

        @keyframes gradient-animation {
            0% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }

            50% {
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }

            100% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
        }

        header {
            background-color: #323f97;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0 0 0 25px;
            text-align: left;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header img {
            width: 30rem;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-right: 10rem;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin: 0 25px;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: chartreuse;
        }

        .toggle-btn {
            display: none;
            /* Initially hide the toggle button */
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 28px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 25px;
            right: 15px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #323f97;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Responsive styles */
        @media (max-width: 1100px) {
            header img {
                width: 20rem;
            }

            nav a {
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin: 0 15px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header img {
                width: 18rem;
            }

            .toggle-btn {
                display: block;
                /* Display the toggle button on small screens */
            }

            nav {
                margin-right: 0rem;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                /* Display the navigation links vertically */
                align-items: center;
                margin-top: 7px;
                display: none;
                /* Initially hide the navigation links on small screens */
                position: absolute;
                top: 50px;
                right: 0px;
                background-color: #323f97;
                padding: 60px;
                animation: slideInOpacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
            }

            @keyframes slideInOpacity {
                from {
                    opacity: 0.5;
                    transform: translateX(100%);
                }

                to {
                    opacity: 1;
                    transform: translateX(0);
                }
            }

            nav a {
                color: #fff;
                text-decoration: none;
                margin: 5px 0;
            }

        }

        .img {
            width: 50px;
        }

        section {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div>
            <img src="userimages/car.png" alt="Icon">
        </div>
        <div class="toggle-btn" onclick="toggleNav()">☰</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="#">About</a>
            <a href="login">Login</a>
            <a href="register">Register</a>
            <a href="/admin"><img class="img" src="userimages/admin_login.png" alt=""></a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Your Car Rental System's Name, where we redefine your travel experience with top-quality and
            reliable car rentals. Our mission is to provide you with a diverse fleet of vehicles, exceptional service,
            and a seamless booking process.</p>

        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Diverse Fleet: From sleek sedans to spacious SUVs, we have a vehicle for every need.</li>
            <li>Quality Assurance: Our vehicles undergo rigorous inspections for your safety.</li>
            <li>User-Friendly Platform: Easily browse, reserve, and manage your bookings online.</li>
            <li>Competitive Pricing: Enjoy transparent pricing with no hidden fees.</li>
            <li>Convenient Locations: Our rental stations are strategically located for your convenience.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>We are available 24/7. Contact our dedicated customer support team for any questions or assistance.</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2023 Your Website Name. All rights reserved.
    </footer>

    <script>
        function toggleNav() {
            var nav = document.querySelector('nav');
            var toggleBtn = document.querySelector('.toggle-btn');

            if (nav.style.display === 'flex' || nav.style.display === '') {
                nav.style.display = 'none';
                toggleBtn.innerHTML = '☰';
            } else {
                nav.style.display = 'flex';
                toggleBtn.innerHTML = '✖';
            }
        }
    </script>

</body>

</html>